[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0050","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0050.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0063","title":"Nortel Contivity HTTP 服务器 cgiproc CGI 脚本任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Nortel Contivity 设备自带的 HTTP 服务器中，cgiproc 这个 CGI 脚本在处理请求时未对用户输入的文件名参数进行合法性与路径校验。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向该 CGI 脚本发送特制的 HTTP 请求，在参数中直接指定目标文件名，从而绕过访问控制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响运行 Contivity HTTP 服务器的相关 Nortel Contivity 设备，攻击仅需网络可达目标服务且无需任何权限，利用方式简单，可导致敏感配置或系统文件泄露，进而威胁设备安全。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0063"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:55.487","remediation":"升级 Nortel Contivity 设备到修复该漏洞的固件/软件版本（咨询 Nortel 获取对应补丁），在无法立即升级时，通过防火墙 ACL 限制仅内网可访问 Contivity 的 HTTP 管理端口，并在 Web 服务器配置中禁用或移除 cgiproc CGI 脚本以阻断任意文件读取路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/938","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f54846af4ec1affce3d519a6791531e8f1f5b8fe/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0063.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0063","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0063.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cf6074d8ac2128dee0a2ac26c5f652ae6527df79/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0063.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jq6c-6f3m-2jr3/GHSA-jq6c-6f3m-2jr3.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0063.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001102.txt","https://github.com/InfoSecWarrior/Vulnerable-Box-Resources/blob/c784bcf63e1ec5c3a0116043d8653d00f0a21a0b/Vulnhub/OZ/oz-1-nikto-80-output.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0050.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0051","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0051.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0064","title":"Nortel Contivity HTTP 服务器 cgiproc 命令注入拒绝服务漏洞","description":"该漏洞位于 Nortel Contivity 1.0 设备内置 HTTP 服务器的 cgiproc CGI 脚本中。该脚本在处理用户请求时未对 URL 中传入的 Shell 元字符（如分号、管道符、反引号等）进行充分过滤与转义，导致远程攻击者可在特制 URL 中植入元字符，使恶意输入被系统 shell 直接解析执行，造成拒绝服务、资源耗尽甚至远程命令执行。攻击者无需身份验证即可通过网络远程触发，影响所有运行 Nortel Contivity 1.0 HTTP 服务器的设备，严重威胁设备稳定性与安全性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0064"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-17","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"建议升级到 Nortel Contivity 修复版本（1.0 后续补丁版本或更高），或联系 Nortel 获取该 CGI 漏洞的安全补丁。短期内可在前置防火墙上限制对 cgiproc CGI 脚本路径的访问，并部署入侵检测规则拦截包含 Shell 元字符的异常 URL 请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7583","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/938","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f54846af4ec1affce3d519a6791531e8f1f5b8fe/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0064.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/N/nortel_cgiproc_dos.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0051.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0061","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0061.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0075","title":"Nosque MsgCore 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Nosque Workshop 开发的 MsgCore 1.9（原名 Super Mail Transfer Package，SMTP）存在内存泄漏漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过在同一个 SMTP 会话中重复发送 HELO、MAIL FROM、RCPT TO 和 DATA 命令，即可消耗目标服务器大量内存资源，最终导致 SMTP 服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 MsgCore 1.9 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0075"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:56.910","remediation":"立即停止使用 Nosque MsgCore 1.9 及更早版本，该产品已停止维护且无安全更新。建议迁移至主流维护的 SMTP 服务器软件（如 Postfix 3.x、Exim 4.x），并在 SMTP 服务端配置连接速率限制和会话超时参数，限制单会话内命令重复次数，同时部署入侵检测规则监控异常 SMTP 命令序列。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/930","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19725","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/83494e95424aced4cfc65648b3019774f7fc51c3/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0075.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0075","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0075.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/03324c0426abad4e55ae7c73b0bba67b9c87e4ea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0075.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4992-6p77-x2cp/GHSA-4992-6p77-x2cp.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0075.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001101.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/20d729d7fbfed4f1ebc4b8a4255bac83c7c5af70/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0061.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0052","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0052.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0066","title":"Website Professional WebSite Pro 目录泄露漏洞","description":"Website Pro 是一款网页制作软件，存在目录路径泄露漏洞。攻击者可通过构造恶意URL请求，诱使服务器返回内部目录路径信息，从而泄露网站实际物理路径布局。该漏洞导致攻击者能够映射服务器文件结构，便于进一步定位目标系统及其潜在弱点。漏洞影响范围包括 WebSite Pro 所有版本，攻击条件较为简单，只需发送包含特殊字符的URL即可触发。利用方式主要有两种：一是手动探测目录路径以收集系统信息，二是利用获取的路径信息为后续攻击提供目标协助，从而可能导致更严重的攻击事件。该漏洞已被证实为真实安全问题，但由于披露时间较早，具体影响范围和利用细节尚需进一步研究。微软官方并未发布针对此漏洞的安全补丁更新。相关的 CWE 分类为 NVD-CWE-Other。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0066"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:55.843","remediation":"建议立即升级 Microsoft Site Server 3.0 至 Service Pack 3 或更高版本，或安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS00-009 提供的安全补丁（KB252693）。若无法立即升级，可在 IIS 中配置 URLScan 过滤器拦截包含 \"..\" 或特殊编码的恶意 URL 请求，或在防火墙层面限制对 Web 服务器管理端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0066","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/2000/CVE-2000-0066.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0066.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0066","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/1694f40643791ff0eb87bac5ac75df888b7163d4/2000/CVE-2000-0066.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0066.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0066.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/website_pro.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--92542821-711e-4123-a0d8-22922cbd91a7.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001100.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0052.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0057","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0057.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0070","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 中 NtImpersonateClientOfPort 本地过程调用（LPC）存在缺陷，允许本地攻击者通过伪造 LPC 端口请求欺骗系统，从而提升权限获取系统特权。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2（高危），攻击向量为本地访问，利用方式为伪造 LPC 端口请求欺骗系统提升权限。Microsoft 已发布补丁修复该漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0070"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:56.313","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS00-003 提供的安全更新，或通过 Windows Update 安装最新 Service Pack。由于该漏洞为本地提权，无法通过网络层面缓解，必须通过打补丁修复。建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本系统以获得长期支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ247869","http://www.bindview.com/security/advisory/adv_NtImpersonate.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/934","http://xforce.iss.net/search.php3?type=2&pattern=nt-spoofed-lpc-port","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-003","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0070.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0070","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0070.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0070.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7c6r-7p46-359r/GHSA-7c6r-7p46-359r.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--99611cb0-8d9a-4f96-8642-43afab66e0c0.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0070.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001098.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0057.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0040","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0040.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0048","title":"Corel Linux OS 1.0 get_it 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Corel Linux OS 1.0 的 get_it 程序存在 PATH 环境变量操纵漏洞。该程序在执行 cp 命令时未使用绝对路径，而是依赖用户提供的 PATH 环境变量来定位可执行文件。本地攻击者可通过修改 PATH 变量，将恶意程序命名为 cp 并置于优先搜索路径中，从而在 get_it 以 root 权限运行时执行任意代码，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 Corel Linux OS 1.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0048"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:53.630","remediation":"立即从 Corel 官方补丁页面 (clos_patch1.htm) 安装安全更新，该补丁修复了 get_it 程序未对 cp 命令路径做安全限制的问题。如无法获取补丁，应限制本地用户对 get_it 程序的执行权限（chmod 700 /usr/bin/get_it），并尽快迁移至仍在维护的 Linux 发行版（如 Ubuntu/Debian），因为 Corel Linux 已停止技术支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://linux.corel.com/support/clos_patch1.htm","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/928","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19723","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b9fb833e196fd08d699d3ef970b517d24cc12600/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0048.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0048","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0048.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1eab609178bfac1fdc1fdc37b8b4d17d9ecf98b7/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0048.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vp5h-j8h3-xvg2/GHSA-vp5h-j8h3-xvg2.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0048.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ec3be0baed1eb129c466b944014a0769e187fd54/2000.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--e16005b9-5841-4a01-90d1-9a5fa7ea2e65.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0040.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0040.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0040.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0072","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0072.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0087","title":"Netscape Communicator nsnotify 明文传输 IMAP 凭据漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 中的 Mail Notification (nsnotify) 工具在连接 IMAP 服务器时未遵循用户的 SSL 配置偏好，始终以明文方式传输数据。攻击者若处于同一网络段，可被动嗅探到 IMAP 认证过程中的用户名和密码，导致邮箱账户凭据泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0087"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-12","updated":"2000-01-12","remediation":"升级至受支持的现代浏览器与邮件客户端，彻底替换已停止维护的 Netscape Communicator；若必须使用遗留系统，应用 Netscape/AOL 发布的安全补丁，并在邮件账户设置中强制启用 IMAP over SSL，禁用明文 IMAP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2024-06-01T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94790377622943&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/4385.php"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0072.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0208","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0208.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0074","title":"PowerScripts PlusMail WebConsole 弱认证漏洞","description":"PowerScripts PlusMail WebConsole 1.0 的 CGI 程序存在弱认证漏洞，其密码文件权限设置不当，导致远程攻击者无需有效凭据即可直接访问或修改密码文件，进而获取系统控制权限。攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制 HTTP 请求，利用不安全的文件权限读取或覆盖密码文件，从而以管理员身份执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 PlusMail WebConsole 1.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，建议升级至最新版本或严格限制密码文件访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0074"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:56.790","remediation":"立即修复 PlusMail 密码文件权限，确保 `password.txt` 等敏感文件权限设置为 600 或更严格，仅允许 Web 服务进程所有者读写。同时升级到 PowerScripts PlusMail 最新版本（如厂商已停止维护，建议迁移至其他受支持的邮件 Web 管理方案）。在 Web 服务器（如 Apache）层面配置访问控制，限制 `/cgi-bin/` 目录仅允许授权 IP 访问，并禁用目录列表功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0074","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20801","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/83494e95424aced4cfc65648b3019774f7fc51c3/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0074.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0074","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/0663522afd1997d13db18aa372c96f4306f457f9/2000/CVE-2000-0074.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0074.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3p8m-qpqj-m94w/GHSA-3p8m-qpqj-m94w.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/03324c0426abad4e55ae7c73b0bba67b9c87e4ea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0074.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/plusmail.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0208.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0208.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0208.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0058","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0058.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0071","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送带有 .ida 或 .idq 扩展名的不存在文件请求，利用服务器返回的错误信息获取网站文档根目录的真实物理路径。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 版本，攻击者无需认证即可利用，获取的路径信息可为进一步攻击（如文件包含、目录遍历）提供基础。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0071"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:56.437","remediation":"立即升级至 IIS 5.0 或更高版本（Windows 2000 及以上系统），该漏洞在 IIS 5.0 中已修复。如无法升级，请在 IIS 管理器中删除 .ida 和 .idq 应用程序映射（网站属性 → 主目录 → 配置 → 应用程序映射），或卸载 Index Server 服务以消除 .ida/.idq 扩展的处理程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94770020309953&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94780058006791&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0071.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0071","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0071.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0071.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-48f3-v7r7-48gh/GHSA-48f3-v7r7-48gh.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/2000/0xxx/cve-2000-0071.yaml","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/iis_anything_idq.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/chihsuan/search-engine/blob/9dcdd3e644469883f53565740f0ba8ff617c5120/Data/E99D88C1-C798-40D7-BB8C-47E6405B9469.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0071.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0058.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0058.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0053","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0053.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0067","title":"CyberCash MCK 不安全临时文件创建本地提权漏洞","description":"CyberCash 多媒体收银机（MCK）在 Unix 系统上创建临时文件时使用了可预测的临时文件名且未采用安全的创建方式（如 mkstemp），攻击者可在 /tmp 目录下预先创建指向敏感文件的符号链接。当 MCK 以更高权限运行并写入该临时文件时，会因符号链接攻击覆盖任意文件，从而导致本地权限提升或拒绝服务。该漏洞无需远程访问，仅需本地用户权限即可利用，影响使用 MCK 的电子商务支付环境。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0067"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-11","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级到 CyberCash 官方修复版本，并将 MCK 运行目录权限收紧为仅属主可写（chmod 700），改用 mkstemp 等安全方式创建临时文件，定期审计 /tmp 下相关符号链接以缓解本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0067","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/main/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0067.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/main/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-98fp-r246-5cjg/GHSA-98fp-r246-5cjg.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0053.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0108","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0108.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0046","title":"Mirabilis ICQ 99b 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Mirabilis ICQ 99b 1.1.1.1 客户端存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，攻击者可通过向目标用户发送包含恶意构造 URL 的 ICQ 消息触发该漏洞，导致在用户系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 ICQ 99b 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害等级高。目前官方已停止对该版本的支持，建议用户升级至最新版本或采取替代通信方案。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0046"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:53.383","remediation":"升级至 ICQ 2000a 或更高版本，该版本已修复 URL 解析缓冲区溢出问题。由于 Mirabilis ICQ 产品线已停止维护且官方服务已关闭，建议迁移至 Signal/Telegram 等现代即时通讯软件作为最终解决方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/929","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19724","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b9fb833e196fd08d699d3ef970b517d24cc12600/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0046.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0046","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0046.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1eab609178bfac1fdc1fdc37b8b4d17d9ecf98b7/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0046.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/icq_vulns.nasl","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/icq_installed.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0046.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--69e67c4e-76b5-4fa4-90c5-5a1691ae56f8.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001093.txt","https://github.com/akabe1/windows_exploit_dowser/blob/11b24e36173cd382721db28581e575faf687d06b/cve_from_exploitdb_website.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0108.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0209","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0209.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0081","title":"微软 Hotmail javascript: 协议跨站脚本漏洞","description":"微软 Hotmail 邮件服务在 2000 年初的版本中，对 HTML 邮件内嵌链接的过滤机制存在缺陷，未能正确拦截 javascript: 协议的 URL。攻击者可将包含 javascript: 伪协议的恶意链接嵌入发送给受害者的邮件中，当受害者点击该链接时，浏览器会在 Hotmail 的会话上下文中执行攻击者构造的脚本。该漏洞影响所有使用当时版本 Hotmail 服务的用户，攻击条件仅需受害者打开并点击恶意邮件中的链接，即可窃取用户 Cookie、会话凭证或冒充用户执行操作，构成典型的跨站脚本（XSS）攻击。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0081"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-10","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级到微软已修复该问题的 Hotmail/Outlook 服务版本，并在邮件网关层对所有入站 HTML 邮件的链接协议进行白名单校验，禁止 javascript:、vbscript: 等危险伪协议，同时启用内容安全策略（CSP）限制脚本执行来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0081","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/2000/CVE-2000-0081.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e268305fd8644994d337819e469d1f89bafde833/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0081.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0209.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0198","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0198.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0061","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 安全区域设置延迟绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0至5.5版本存在安全区域设置延迟漏洞。当浏览器将文档加载到窗口中时，IE不会立即更新该文档的安全区域设置，而是等到文档完全加载后才进行切换。远程攻击者可利用这一时序差异，在文档加载过程中通过构造恶意页面，使JavaScript代码在与目标文档不同的安全区域上下文中执行，从而绕过区域间的安全隔离策略。该漏洞影响IE 4.0、4.0.1、5.0、5.0.1及5.5版本，攻击者仅需诱使用户访问恶意网页即可触发，无需额外权限。建议升级至已修复此漏洞的Internet Explorer版本或迁移至现代浏览器。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0061"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-07T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:55.253","remediation":"由于Internet Explorer 4.x/5.x已停止支持超过20年，建议立即迁移至Microsoft Edge或其他现代浏览器。若必须在遗留系统中保留IE，应至少升级至IE 11。临时缓解措施：将所有外部站点添加至\"受限制的站点\"区域并禁用该区域的活动脚本执行；启用增强安全配置以降低默认安全级别；在组策略中禁用跨域访问和脚本插件加载。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/923","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f54846af4ec1affce3d519a6791531e8f1f5b8fe/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0061.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0061","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0061.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cf6074d8ac2128dee0a2ac26c5f652ae6527df79/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0061.json","https://github.com/biggerwing/nsfocus-rsas-knowledge-base/blob/156208b301d4649ead13cd15f827830d08245b89/example","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2w55-jm9h-8pcw/GHSA-2w55-jm9h-8pcw.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17b