d122acc94/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0044.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/490d6657aaeb62053fddc3213da299eb1e656f38/api/2000/CVE-2000-0044.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0044.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0106.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0070","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0070.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0084","title":"CuteFTP 密码信息弱加密存储漏洞","description":"CuteFTP 使用弱加密算法在 tree.dat 文件中存储密码信息，导致本地攻击者可通过读取该文件并解密其中的弱加密数据，获取用户的 FTP 服务器登录凭据。该漏洞影响所有使用受影响版本 CuteFTP 的用户，攻击者需具备本地文件系统访问权限才能读取 tree.dat 文件，随后利用弱加密特性还原明文密码，进而接管受害者的 FTP 账号。CVSS 评分 5.0，属中等危害等级。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0084"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:58.020","remediation":"建议立即将 CuteFTP 升级到 v8.6 及更高版本，该版本修复了 tree.dat 文件的弱加密漏洞；或在安全模式下使用新版本并重新导入密码。禁用旧版中的“兼容模式”和“明文密码存储”选项，加强认证失败后的账户锁定机制。通过 Windows Update 设置每日备份本地密码文件或使用第三方安全密码管理器，如 LastPass 1.0 等现代工具，彻底淘汰旧版 CuteFTP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0084","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e244b55bdff85b2483c0e6a7cecd12f8bee0df6e/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0084.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0084","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/dd092b3aeda9cc5d8bd2754d447adf54a208720a/2000/CVE-2000-0084.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0084.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2c8m-gphg-q96w/GHSA-2c8m-gphg-q96w.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0ea6b1a12984